ther they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/134964/', '', 'Aducanumab', 'Phenelzine, Duloxetine, Tranylcypromine, Desvenlafaxine, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Tryptophan, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, More', 1767369485);
